Package: mbspls
Type: Package
Title: Multi-Block Sparse Partial Least Squares
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-07-07
Authors@R: 
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implementation of Multi-Block Sparse Partial Least Squares (MBSPLS) 
    for integrative analysis of multiple data blocks. The package provides 
    functionality for dimensionality reduction, feature selection, and 
    correlation analysis between multiple high-dimensional datasets. It supports 
    cross-validation, permutation testing, bootstrapping, and hyperparameter 
    optimization with parallel processing capabilities.
